other_tests.procedure_name: CT Scan of the Abdomen and Pelvis
other_tests.findings: Gallbladder wall thickening and trace perihepatic fluid; no evidence of pneumoperitoneum or of a foreign body.

other_tests.procedure_name: Lateral Image of the Right Elbow
other_tests.findings: Posterior dislocation of the elbow with impaction of the olecranon process of the ulna into the distal humerus outside the olecranon fossa.

other_tests.procedure_name: Anteroposterior Image of the Right Elbow
other_tests.findings: Confirmed dislocation of the elbow with malalignment of the ulnotrochlear and radiocapitellar joints.

other_tests.procedure_name: Lateral and Anteroposterior Images of the Right Elbow after Closed Reduction
other_tests.findings: Normal alignment of the ulnotrochlear and radiocapitellar joints.

other_tests.procedure_name: Lateral Image of the Left Elbow
other_tests.findings: Posterior dislocation of the elbow with a fragment from a displaced fracture of the trochlea.

other_tests.procedure_name: Lateral Image of the Left Elbow after Reduction and Casting
other_tests.findings: Reduction achieved and a long-arm circumferential fiberglass cast was placed.
